{"tid":774570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 宋皇臺站亦有居民投訴疑受工程影響，大廈出現沉降","createTime":"2018-08-10T12:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T12:30:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f87a1167b70db560c94cf4f83577564d8b418e63","tid":774570,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中線土瓜灣站地盤工程疑令附近樓宇出現沉降問題，多個政黨昨到馬頭圍道一帶唐樓視察，要求港鐵在確定大廈安全前，立即停工。有區議員透露繼土瓜灣站後，鄰近的宋皇臺站亦有居民投訴疑受工程影響，大廈出現沉降，反映問題有蔓延迹象。九龍城區議會下周將召開特別會議，邀請港鐵及煤氣公司等代表出席，要求港鐵交代沙中線全部車站的沉降數據及影響。另有政黨昨到現場收集居民簽名，要求立法會復會後，以《權力及特權條例》徹查整條沙中線的工程問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/201007_406e1c53be5af523247c4bb648cd54a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F201007_406e1c53be5af523247c4bb648cd54a9.png&h=cd9ad3cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180810/00176_012.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180810%2F00176_012.html&d=Y3F1bRh%2Bt2YTIYe7DglWXQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c3f4a7b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180810/00176_012.html</a>"},{"pid":"394260e2b6292c733c51825119c5dae1e2ae4adf","tid":774570,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:13:28.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"0995915c45669ac7aa34dadad0523cbd8195200e","tid":774570,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}